# Asset License Information

## Poly Haven Environment Maps

This folder contains environment maps from [Poly Haven](https://polyhaven.com). These assets are provided under the CC0 (Creative Commons Zero) license with the following terms:

### CC0 License Overview
- These assets are completely free to use for any purpose
- No attribution is required (although it is appreciated)
- They can be used in commercial projects
- They can be modified and redistributed
- There are no restrictions on how they are used

### Source
These environment maps are from Poly Haven (https://polyhaven.com), a platform that provides high-quality, free, CC0-licensed 3D assets.

### Acknowledgment
While the CC0 license does not require attribution, we appreciate Poly Haven and its contributors for providing these high-quality resources.